---
description: dlt ingestion project guidance
globs:
  - "**/*.py"
alwaysApply: false
---
- Keep extraction logic in `@dlt.resource` functions.
- Use `dlt.config.value` for non-secret config values and `dlt.secrets.value` for credentials.
- Keep pipeline execution in a `run()` function and call it from `if __name__ == "__main__"`.
- For APIs without YAML scaffold, define endpoint URL and auth in `.dlt/config.toml` and `.dlt/secrets.toml`.
